{
  "stem": "22685.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They never saw a Jew, but for them, a Jew was some kind of-- I became-- again, which was a little bit luck, or whatever it is-- the bookkeeper of the-- not the bookkeeper, but the function of a bookkeeper, and the function of a-- I have to explain the system, how the whole system worked in Russia.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "People weren't paid for work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were-- they were paid in form of working days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They had an algorithm-- if you cut, let's say, a 10 square meter of field, you get one working day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You cut-- you cut 20 or 30, you have the multiple of that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was the one who had to check what other people were producing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was part of my job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- and we were settled, everything was going well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Until the Germans started to come closer to Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we knew, we don't-- we lived on the Don, Don River.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was no other communication except by river, because the next station was like 20 miles away, and there was no transportation, private, and everything.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the only way to go out of there was by the Don.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Don freezes in winter, so we had to go out before the winter.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, thousands of people were waiting in line and-- and-- and we didn't have a chance to do it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But God works in mysterious ways.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It came-- a barge with coal-- so the manager of the station told us, if you unload the barge--the coal barge, you'll have a trip to Stalingrad with the barge.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, I don't have to tell you we took the job.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whatever-- it took us a day and a half.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We unloaded the coal.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
